                    </p>
                    <div class="hero-cta">
                        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Book Free Demo</a>
                        <a href="#features" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">See Features</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hero-meta">
                        <div class="avatar-stack">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1502685104226-ee32379fefbe?auto=format&fit=crop&w=80&q=80" alt="Parent">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1524504388940-b1c1722653e1?auto=format&fit=crop&w=80&q=80" alt="Parent">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544723795-3fb6469f5b39?auto=format&fit=crop&w=80&q=80" alt="Parent">
