                    <h3 class="features-cta-title">See Our Platform in Action.</h3>
                    <p class="features-cta-subtitle">Start Your Journey with Peace of Mind!</p>
                </div>
                <div class="features-cta-buttons">
                    <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-white-cta">
                        <span>Book Free Demo</span>
                        <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i>
                    </a>
                    <a href="mailto:kidzview@support.com" class="btn btn-outline-cta">
                        <span>Contact Us</span>
                        <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!-- How Parents Love KidzView -->
    <section id="platform" class="pricing">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2 class="impact-title">
                    Complete Platform
                    <span class="impact-sub">for Modern PlaySchools</span>
                </h2>
            </div>
            <div class="pricing-grid">
                <div class="price-card">
                    <div class="price-pill">For Teachers</div>
                    <h3>Website Portal</h3>
                    <div class="testimonial-content">
                        <p class="testimonial-quote">A comprehensive web portal where teachers can update student information, send daily notifications for school updates, and write to specific parents for any enquiries. Manage everything from one central dashboard.</p>
                        <div class="testimonial-footer">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1573496359142-b8d87734a5a2?auto=format&fit=crop&w=150&q=80" alt="Teacher Portal" class="testimonial-avatar">
                            <div>
                                <h4>Teacher Dashboard</h4>
                                <span>Manage & Communicate</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="price-card featured">
                    <div class="price-pill">For Parents</div>
                    <h3>Mobile App</h3>
                    <div class="testimonial-content">
                        <p class="testimonial-quote">Parents access everything through our mobile app - watch live streams of their children, receive all notifications from teachers, and stay connected with the school. All updates from the web portal reach parents instantly.</p>
                        <div class="testimonial-footer">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512941937669-90a1b58e7e9c?auto=format&fit=crop&w=150&q=80" alt="Mobile App" class="testimonial-avatar">
                            <div>
                                <h4>Parent App</h4>
                                <span>Watch & Stay Connected</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="price-card">
                    <div class="price-pill">Security First</div>
                    <h3>Privacy Concern</h3>
                    <div class="testimonial-content">
                        <p class="testimonial-quote">All streams are end-to-end encrypted for maximum security. Videos are automatically and permanently deleted after 30 days. Parents can download and save streams during this period.</p>
                        <div class="testimonial-footer">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1563013544-824ae1b704d3?auto=format&fit=crop&w=150&q=80" alt="Security" class="testimonial-avatar">
                            <div>
                                <h4>Bank-Grade Security</h4>
                                <span>Encrypted & Auto-Delete</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonials -->
    <section id="reviews" class="testimonials">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2 class="section-title">Why choose <span class="italic-text light-text">KidzView</span></h2>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonials-bento">
                <div class="bento-card large dark">
                    <span class="bento-label">FULLY CUSTOMIZABLE</span>
                    <div class="bento-content">
                        <p class="bento-quote">We don't stop at standard features. If your school needs more customization—whether it's additional integrations, custom reporting, or unique workflows—we make it happen. Your vision, our technology.</p>
                        <div class="bento-author">
                            <div>
                                <h4>Unlimited Customization</h4>
                                <span>Tailored to Your Needs</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bento-image">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1454165804606-c3d57bc86b40?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="Customization">
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="bento-card stat yellow">
                    <span class="bento-label">AFFORDABLE PRICING</span>
                    <div class="bento-stat-content">
                        <h3 class="bento-stat-number">₹0</h3>
                        <p class="bento-stat-text">initial setup cost. We work on very competitive pricing based on your business scale."</p>
