                    <div class="bento-decorative">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1450101499163-c8848c66ca85?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80" alt="Support">
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="bento-card large light">
                    <span class="bento-label">COMPETITIVE ADVANTAGE</span>
                    <p class="bento-quote-large">Our pricing model scales with your business. Pay based on your school size and grow without worrying about fixed costs. Perfect for startups and established institutions alike.</p>
                    <div class="bento-author">
