            <div class="cta-content">
                <h2 class="cta-title">Ready to Make Parents Happy? <span class="italic-text light-text">for peace of mind</span></h2>
                <p class="cta-description">
                    Looking to elevate your PlaySchool? We craft immersive live streaming experiences that captivate parents, build trust, and make your school unforgettable in every interaction.
                </p>
                <a href="mailto:kidzview@support.com" class="cta-button">
                    <span>Book Your Free Demo</span>
                    <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i>
